#tabspy

this is the documentation for tabspy package

## Installation:
```
pip install tabspy
```

## Usage
Code:
```
import tabspy.utils as ut
import tabspy.strategy.strategy as st

a = ut.welcome()
b = st.Strategy()
b.welcome()
```
Output:
```
Welcome TABSPY : tabspy >> ta >> utils
Welcome None : tabspy >> ta >> strategy
```
